column5: I remember it being dicussed not too long ago, but just wondering which weekend was decided on and the location?  Looking forward to this if it is still going down.
when ever it is i'll be there
i tried to do a search but came up with nothing either
Would this be the tread your looking for Skeeter:   http://www.ofncommunity.com/forums/index.p...=26289&st=0    Don

So, it looks like the old thread kinda died.  Ummm...let's see what happens if we pick a date like...  FEBRUARY 29th.  It's a Sunday.  I'll finally get to cross BOQ off my list...if folks wanna make it a weekend thing, go for it...I have to work Saturday, so LakerJessy and I'd drive out Sat. night and stay over, or just leave REAL early Sunday morning from Mississauga.  Anybody???
I could probably do that, and bring a few others as well.  Confirm a date/time, and I'll put it in my calendar!
I might just be able to make this one, my only problem is by the time i get a hole cut big enough to troll i am to tired to fish
i heard theres been some nice perch to be had there lately
There are nice ones like this one to be had Kerrby.    Next time use your own rod to catch MY JUMBO's.....even if I am eating lunch when one happens to bite!
